name: Smol Bun
description: BUN began as a test token and has evolved into a community-driven meme token centered around the concept of a small rabbit — “tis ist de smollest bun on Solana.” The smol rabbit is more than a symbol; it reflects the project's inclusive and playful spirit. BUN encourages collaboration and fun among its community members, promoting decentralized participation and engagement within the Solana ecosystem.
